She smirked with a sly & sultry grin upon her face. Indeed, she loved to hear 
those words. 

But she replied to his question. "Someone is obviously telling her something. 
I have noticed that she is distracted. Ever since we left the base. However, 
she tried very hard to do her duty. Thus far, she is a good warrior." 

But she smiled again, as his previous words rang in her head. 

--part1_178.1b3ee8f0.2c05b77e_boundary
